<i class="Summary5 fa fa-book"></i>
<a class="Summary6" href="#creation-d-un-plugin-pour-qt-designer_notes-sur-la-macro-qdesigner_widget_export">Notes sur la macro&nbsp;QDESIGNER_WIDGET_EXPORT</a>
</div>
<div class="GSummary21 Summary4">
<i class="Summary5 fa fa-book"></i>
<a class="Summary6" href="#creation-d-un-plugin-pour-qt-designer_notes-sur-la-macro-q_interfaces-">Notes sur la macro Q_INTERFACES&nbsp;</a>
